{"tid":734654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾百中小企登報拒撤機制　商會：勞顧會不代表我","createTime":"2018-07-08T23:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T07:15:48.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce50867214d9d043d6e6b5b495acb00dde2b5c7","tid":734654,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T23:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1610025/org/17f85b49232d6c34bae5871d9064de31.jpg/9RLKgbe62PwWugrFAjYiS4ljW3WB9iV1yAaxwcgGscE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1610025%2Forg%2F17f85b49232d6c34bae5871d9064de31.jpg%2F9RLKgbe62PwWugrFAjYiS4ljW3WB9iV1yAaxwcgGscE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=7f27a765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撤強積金對沖再遇阻力，代表150個中小企商會的香港各界商會聯席會議今（4日）再登報發聯合聲明，表明強烈反對勞顧會未有取得商界同意前，便與政府達成共識，決定落實取消對沖，認為在內的資方委員意見不具代表性。<br />\n<br />\n聯席重申港府需永續包底，與商界共同承擔責任，又否認為與五大商會「互扯貓尾」，不排除再有下一波行動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1610027/org/fbf772cedcaf31c252aab7ce0a1e2e6c.jpg/8MA5N5AWdKYPupLaQoyBFrlCSyjxG0Z3WJYnY1iWJ2M?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1610027%2Forg%2Ffbf772cedcaf31c252aab7ce0a1e2e6c.jpg%2F8MA5N5AWdKYPupLaQoyBFrlCSyjxG0Z3WJYnY1iWJ2M%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=78923459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港各界商會聯席會議登報發聯合聲明，反對取消對沖。（陳淑霞攝）<br />\n<br />\n香港各界商會聯席會議月前已聯同逾百間中小企登報表達反對立場，亦有與勞福局局長羅致光會晤表達意見，五大商會當時亦站同一陣綫，要求港府作永久承擔。不過勞顧會上月13日開會後，資方代表委員突釋出善意，勞資雙方更罕有全體會見傳媒，指已與政府達成共識，同意取消對沖，不過此舉惹來部分中小企不滿，認為未能照顧聲音。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1610905/org/07f4594c3611310d62d941244a425d9e.JPG/eFB_u5LODrjCcxLsgxQPfqVMPBgMdADDpBvbu6Qb27s?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1610905%2Forg%2F07f4594c3611310d62d941244a425d9e.JPG%2FeFB_u5LODrjCcxLsgxQPfqVMPBgMdADDpBvbu6Qb27s%3Fv%3Dw960&h=7b303834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳其鑣否認聯席與五大商會「互扯貓尾」，又指勞顧會代表性低。（羅君豪攝）<br />\n<br />\n聯席會議召集人陳其鑣認為，勞顧會僅屬諮詢組織，在內的商界委員代表性低，亦毋須強制諮詢業界， 「有少少係個人意見，佢哋自己圍內都未必問得好清楚，有些少黑箱作業。」<br />\n<br />\n積金局最新數據顯示，去年全港打工仔被沖走逾43億元強積金供款，再創新高，陳反駁，整個強積金制度累積9千多億元，已發放6百億元，被抵銷金額僅佔當中5%，他又強調，「唔係沖咗，而係提早拎返筆錢。」<br />\n<br />\n他認為，政府所提方案屬初步構思，特首林鄭月娥亦未落實細節，認為尚有空間改變形勢。他否認與五大商會「互扯貓尾」，又不認為會造成分裂，「咁我哋有聲音，就要表達。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1610032/org/6d7e3d771c056c1c14d8883441d1b440.jpg/f7VtN2KUUwCvxcdTklGK7ETzRhnKfd8NC9BaJQvQWiU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1610032%2Forg%2F6d7e3d771c056c1c14d8883441d1b440.jpg%2Ff7VtN2KUUwCvxcdTklGK7ETzRhnKfd8NC9BaJQvQWiU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=2e0bc251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港各界商會聯席會議登報發聯合聲明，反對取消對沖。（都市日報截圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1610947/org/47d2a9a0ee6ba3f02054f5351864296a.JPG/xxATY2gybDKPYTOqfzTGVVf4sly5H3ZcHp7i3h6e4t4?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1610947%2Forg%2F47d2a9a0ee6ba3f02054f5351864296a.JPG%2FxxATY2gybDKPYTOqfzTGVVf4sly5H3ZcHp7i3h6e4t4%3Fv%3Dw960&h=6523711b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1610948/org/21364b48b15fd0a4d7634278fcb54d7f.JPG/Qs3vwWjI-r5gxZQZDAYuyKwmTJy38HEvEOT1RxDk9Uc?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1610948%2Forg%2F21364b48b15fd0a4d7634278fcb54d7f.JPG%2FQs3vwWjI-r5gxZQZDAYuyKwmTJy38HEvEOT1RxDk9Uc%3Fv%3Dw960&h=ec312138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自由黨立法會議員鍾國斌指，五大商會雖於勞顧會有代表角色，但不及聯席具代表性，因已累計有150個跨行業商會加入，會員數以萬計，促政府勿忽視聯席聲音，「再拖落去，已經唔係勞資問題，而係商界存亡問題。」<br />\n<br />\n聯席會議秘書長沈運龍認為，今屆政府如同港英政府般短視，又指已回歸21年，政府已是永久性，不明白何以在撤對沖一事上，拒作永久承擔， 又認為初步構思難明，「連精算師、麻雀王都唔明白呢個咁嘅離地方案。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：陳淑霞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/206636/%E6%92%A4%E5%BC%B7%E7%A9%8D%E9%87%91%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96-%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E4%BC%81%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B1%E6%8B%92%E6%92%A4%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6-%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83-%E5%8B%9E%E9%A1%A7%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%88%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F206636%2F%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%25A9%258D%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B2%2596-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BC%2581%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%2592%25A4%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2588%25B6-%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%258B%259E%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2588%2591&d=%2BTNpM2DZD3j0HRxZHuxcIP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a3913bd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/206636/%E6%92%A4%E5%BC%B7%E7%A9%8D%E9%87%91%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96-%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E4%BC%81%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B1%E6%8B%92%E6%92%A4%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6-%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83-%E5%8B%9E%E9%A1%A7%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%88%91</a>"},{"pid":"a472648f5da867641e29303898c6908578cdeb7b","tid":734654,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T23:53:03.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"9e30b0b526447f4c1b4e07067a947b17715f6726","tid":734654,"uid":25952,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T23:56:27.000Z","msg":"對沖機制 對自己有利 有益嘛 緊係反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無錢唔好學人做生意啦"},{"pid":"de110148b5a89e404d10bba6ae4dea394bb55c8e","tid":734654,"uid":60648,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T00:39:27.000Z","msg":"點解唔檢討下自己先<br />\n點解人地可以自己唔可以下<br />\n發揮獅子山下精神<br />\n唔好郁d 就嗌山嗌死<br />\n咁唔捱得點出黎社會做野啊"},{"pid":"0a14e77b77a14baf24ba49c873fd53d4c7d13a34","tid":734654,"uid":39200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T00:51:53.000Z","msg":"好想知有邊百五間"},{"pid":"914fff29f37f100a14acf15635e5311703e982ab","tid":734654,"uid":54733,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201